603
00:29:51,640 --> 00:29:52,640
Do you still believe the success rate

604
00:29:52,640 --> 00:29:53,400
was very high?

605
00:29:56,200 --> 00:29:57,040
As you said,

606
00:29:57,840 --> 00:29:59,160
since the situation had changed,

607
00:29:59,720 --> 00:30:00,880
it needed to be reassessed.

608
00:30:02,040 --> 00:30:02,560
We

609
00:30:02,960 --> 00:30:05,400
consulted Chief Xue and Chief Liao,

610
00:30:05,560 --> 00:30:06,320
and also sought opinions

611
00:30:06,640 --> 00:30:07,880
