612
00:30:08,320 --> 00:30:09,440
Judging from the fetus's

613
00:30:09,480 --> 00:30:10,480
indications at the time,

614
00:30:10,840 --> 00:30:11,880
the success rate of the surgery

615
00:30:12,160 --> 00:30:13,160
