626
00:30:31,760 --> 00:30:33,520
That is like driving without a license.

627
00:30:34,280 --> 00:30:34,880
Chief Zhou.

628
00:30:36,160 --> 00:30:36,560
So,

629
00:30:37,440 --> 00:30:38,800
