Don't evade it.

633
00:30:54,640 --> 00:30:55,600
That question is unreasonable.

634
00:30:56,800 --> 00:30:57,560
Who would fly a plane

635
00:30:57,640 --> 00:30:58,600
in a thunderstorm for no reason?

636
00:30:59,800 --> 00:31:01,040
It was because the situation was urgent.

637
00:31:02,640 --> 00:31:03,560
Everyone here is a doctor.

638
00:31:04,280 --> 00:31:05,120
I don't think Professor Fang

639
00:31:05,200 --> 00:31:05,720
did anything wrong.

640
00:31:06,440 --> 00:31:07,280
In that situation,

641
00:31:07,280 --> 00:31:08,200
if the surgery hadn't been done,

642
00:31:08,320 --> 00:31:09,600
the fetus definitely couldn't have been saved.

643
00:31:09,760 --> 00:31:10,040
If it were me,

644
00:31:10,040 --> 00:31:11,040
I would have operated too.

645
00:31:12,280 --> 00:31:13,280
I support Professor Fang.

646
00:31:17,200 --> 00:31:17,600
Lin Yi.

647
00:31:17,920 --> 00:31:18,600
Sit down first.

648
00:31:19,240 --> 00:31:20,560
Let's hear what Chief Zhou has to say.

649
00:31:26,840 --> 00:31:27,440
Chief Zhou.

650
00:31:28,880 --> 00:31:30,480
You brought the patient here.

651
00:31:31,640 --> 00:31:32,720
You're also the project lead.

652
00:31:33,520 --> 00:31:35,280
Your attitude and position

653
00:31:35,640 --> 00:31:37,160
affect the hospital's

654
00:31:37,520 --> 00:31:39,640
determination of Professor Fang's liability.

655
00:31:40,760 --> 00:31:41,400
They also affect

656
00:31:41,840 --> 00:31:44,760
the future of your congenital heart project.

657
00:31:53,320 --> 00:31:54,200
I do not support it.

658
00:32:11,640 --> 00:32:13,320
I do not support Professor Fang's actions.

659
00:32:15,840 --> 00:32:17,040
I believe this was

660
00:32:17,640 --> 00:32:18,280
seriously irresponsible

661
00:32:18,920 --> 00:32:19,800
to the patient, the family,

662
00:32:19,880 --> 00:32:21,160
