668
00:33:18,160 --> 00:33:18,840
Begin.

669
00:33:20,720 --> 00:33:21,600
Regarding the recent

670
00:33:22,280 --> 00:33:23,520
medical incident

671
00:33:23,960 --> 00:33:25,120
