678
00:33:36,840 --> 00:33:37,480
The investigation confirmed that

679
00:33:37,720 --> 00:33:39,080
the operating physician, Dr. Fang Zhuqing,

680
00:33:39,400 --> 00:33:40,840
disregarded standard medical procedures

681
00:33:41,040 --> 00:33:41,840
and illegally used

682
00:33:42,200 --> 00:33:43,600
