684
00:33:44,840 --> 00:33:46,200
The health authority

685
00:33:46,840 --> 00:33:47,600
has ordered her

686
00:33:48,040 --> 00:33:50,440
to suspend medical practice for six months.

687
00:33:52,120 --> 00:33:53,040
Dongli Hospital

688
00:33:53,920 --> 00:33:54,840
has received a warning penalty.

689
00:33:55,520 --> 00:33:56,960
Other members involved in the surgery

690
00:33:57,320 --> 00:33:58,200
