695
00:34:04,920 --> 00:34:06,880
by this incident.

696
00:34:07,520 --> 00:34:08,880
After deliberation,

697
00:34:09,240 --> 00:34:10,080
the hospital has decided

698
00:34:10,520 --> 00:34:11,280
to terminate,

699
00:34:11,840 --> 00:34:12,880
