700
00:34:13,080 --> 00:34:14,160
all cooperative relationships with Dr.
Fang Zhuqing.

701
00:34:14,480 --> 00:34:15,080
Stop watching.

702
00:34:20,440 --> 00:34:22,320
How could the punishment be so severe?

703
00:34:24,040 --> 00:34:25,720
And they made my brother announce it.

704
00:34:26,960 --> 00:34:27,840
Don't panic yet.

705
00:34:28,600 --> 00:34:30,040
There must be something behind this

706
00:34:30,040 --> 00:34:30,760
