707
00:34:31,080 --> 00:34:31,840
If I see him later,

708
00:34:31,840 --> 00:34:32,600
I'll ask him directly.

709
00:34:44,520 --> 00:34:45,840
With Aunt Fang going through this,

710
00:34:46,840 --> 00:34:47,440
