712
00:34:48,880 --> 00:34:50,080
She likely doesn't want to answer.

713
00:34:57,200 --> 00:34:58,760
Mom, where are you now?

714
00:35:56,320 --> 00:35:58,840
I'm at the temple.

715
00:35:58,960 --> 00:36:00,800
I got one for each of you.

716
00:36:02,760 --> 00:36:03,520
Thank you, Mom.

717
00:36:03,520 --> 00:36:04,280
Thank you, Aunt Fang.

718
00:36:04,280 --> 00:36:05,040
Thank you, Professor Fang.

719
00:36:05,440 --> 00:36:07,080
You've all worked so hard.

720
00:36:08,080 --> 00:36:09,120
It's for your safety and peace.

721
00:36:16,280 --> 00:36:18,080
You're back at Dongli now.

722
00:36:18,520 --> 00:36:19,440
Keep going.

723
00:36:22,120 --> 00:36:22,880
Get back to work.

724
00:36:25,080 --> 00:36:25,640
I'm okay.

725
00:36:31,840 --> 00:36:32,440
Xiaofeng.

726
00:36:34,080 --> 00:36:34,760
When the time comes,

727
00:36:35,520 --> 00:36:36,200
during the investigation

728
00:36:36,480 --> 00:36:37,080
and the inquiry,

729
00:36:37,600 --> 00:36:38,880
you must say what

730
00:36:38,880 --> 00:36:39,840
