734
00:36:48,040 --> 00:36:48,720
Do you hear me?

735
00:36:50,880 --> 00:36:51,440
Go on.

736
00:36:52,840 --> 00:36:53,560
I'm fine.

737
00:37:16,640 --> 00:37:17,560
We must resolutely prevent

738
00:37:17,920 --> 00:37:19,600
such incidents from happening again.

739
00:37:21,400 --> 00:37:22,600
This wasn't easy for Xiaofeng.

740
00:37:22,920 --> 00:37:23,960
Indeed.

741
00:37:24,720 --> 00:37:25,520
Right now,

742
00:37:26,840 --> 00:37:27,520
have the patient and her family

743
00:37:28,080 --> 00:37:29,120
