745
00:37:31,080 --> 00:37:32,160
Not for now.

746
00:37:33,120 --> 00:37:33,920
They probably accepted it.

747
00:37:34,520 --> 00:37:35,520
In addition to what's mentioned in the notice,

748
00:37:36,400 --> 00:37:37,800
