764
00:38:00,640 --> 00:38:01,920
The mother is doing fine.

765
00:38:02,520 --> 00:38:03,720
She just needs time to recover.

766
00:38:04,280 --> 00:38:04,880
As for the baby,

767
00:38:04,880 --> 00:38:05,920
