771
00:38:10,400 --> 00:38:11,280
So,

772
00:38:11,840 --> 00:38:12,960
the handling decision

773
00:38:13,160 --> 00:38:14,880
must be followed up and fully implemented.

774
00:38:15,880 --> 00:38:16,840
During the three months

775
00:38:16,840 --> 00:38:17,760
