776
00:38:18,560 --> 00:38:20,200
we must care more for the patient

777
00:38:20,480 --> 00:38:22,240
and her family in daily life.

778
00:38:23,080 --> 00:38:25,400
Help with whatever we can.

779
00:38:26,120 --> 00:38:26,800
Of course.

780
00:38:28,520 --> 00:38:29,560
But now that

781
00:38:30,200 --> 00:38:31,520
the notice has been issued,

782
00:38:32,080 --> 00:38:33,240
has Professor Fang

783
00:38:33,800 --> 00:38:34,800
