788
00:38:44,400 --> 00:38:45,920
The punishment has been issued.

789
00:38:45,920 --> 00:38:47,400
The notice has been announced.

790
00:38:47,560 --> 00:38:48,720
Now the operating doctor

791
00:38:48,720 --> 00:38:50,080
