793
00:38:51,400 --> 00:38:52,600
There is no reason to refuse.

794
00:38:53,400 --> 00:38:53,920
Xuemei.

795
00:38:54,280 --> 00:38:55,120
Professor Fang is here.

796
00:38:56,200 --> 00:38:57,520
Professor Fang is here. Take it easy.

797
00:38:57,520 --> 00:38:58,480
Professor Fang, careful.

798
00:38:59,240 --> 00:39:00,200
Don't get up. Don't get up.

799
00:39:00,720 --> 00:39:01,280
It's okay. It's okay.

800
00:39:03,480 --> 00:39:04,400
How are you, Xuemei?

801
00:39:05,200 --> 00:39:06,160
Pretty good.

802
00:39:09,440 --> 00:39:11,880
We went to see the baby yesterday.

803
00:39:12,320 --> 00:39:13,520
He's doing pretty well too.

804
00:39:19,080 --> 00:39:20,200
I know what that child

805
00:39:20,720 --> 00:39:21,840
