806
00:39:23,160 --> 00:39:24,520
I'm sorry I couldn't help you keep her.

807
00:39:24,600 --> 00:39:25,560
I'm truly sorry.

808
00:39:28,400 --> 00:39:29,720
I just wasn't blessed enough.

809
00:39:32,440 --> 00:39:33,040
Professor Fang.

810
00:39:35,600 --> 00:39:37,480
This is my eldest daughter.

811
00:39:38,280 --> 00:39:39,320
Her name is Nini.

812
00:39:41,320 --> 00:39:42,400
She's beautiful.

813
00:39:43,320 --> 00:39:43,880
Yes.

814
00:39:45,400 --> 00:39:48,120
I dreamed of her again last night.

815
00:39:51,400 --> 00:39:53,920
I told her I was sorry.

816
00:39:55,600 --> 00:39:57,200
Mommy couldn't catch you.

817
00:40:03,200 --> 00:40:04,840
This time, she didn't cry.

818
00:40:05,320 --> 00:40:07,280
She even wiped away my tears.

819
00:40:10,160 --> 00:40:11,800
She... she knew that we

820
00:40:11,800 --> 00:40:13,400
had all done everything we could.

821
00:40:16,200 --> 00:40:18,280
I even touched her face.

822
00:40:18,400 --> 00:40:20,200
It was soft and warm.

823
00:40:21,040 --> 00:40:22,840
I held her so tightly,

824
00:40:22,840 --> 00:40:23,640
for such a long time.

825
00:40:23,640 --> 00:40:24,920
I told her,

826
00:40:26,040 --> 00:40:27,520
