827
00:40:27,560 --> 00:40:28,560
We'll be mother and daughter again.

828
00:40:28,560 --> 00:40:29,800
She promised me.

829
00:40:29,840 --> 00:40:31,080
She... she didn't blame me.

830
00:40:31,080 --> 00:40:31,840
She promised me.

831
00:40:35,880 --> 00:40:37,720
You were so brave the whole way.

832
00:40:38,400 --> 00:40:40,160
Your child knows how much you loved her.

833
00:40:40,760 --> 00:40:42,200
You never gave up on her.

834
00:40:42,920 --> 00:40:45,400
This journey just made you suffer too much.

835
00:40:46,520 --> 00:40:47,400
Professor Fang.

836
00:40:48,400 --> 00:40:49,160
Thank you.

837
00:40:51,320 --> 00:40:52,880
I feel that this time,

838
00:40:53,880 --> 00:40:55,840
I truly said goodbye to her.

839
00:40:57,960 --> 00:40:59,720
I have no regrets now.

840
00:41:00,840 --> 00:41:01,640
Thank you.

841
00:41:02,840 --> 00:41:04,160
But because of us,

842
00:41:05,200 --> 00:41:06,440
