843
00:41:06,440 --> 00:41:07,800
I'm sorry, Professor Fang.

844
00:41:09,200 --> 00:41:10,080
I don't feel wronged.

845
00:41:10,400 --> 00:41:11,200
I'm sorry.

846
00:41:11,200 --> 00:41:11,840
Thank you.

847
00:41:14,600 --> 00:41:15,560
Don't cry.

848
00:41:23,800 --> 00:41:25,480
Why are your hands so cold?

849
00:41:25,520 --> 00:41:26,440
I'm fine.

850
00:41:27,280 --> 00:41:28,240
Now that I've seen Xuemei,

851
00:41:28,240 --> 00:41:29,520
I can be at ease.

852
00:41:30,280 --> 00:41:31,640
Has my brother contacted you?

853
00:41:31,880 --> 00:41:33,640
I kept messaging him, but he hasn't replied.

854
00:41:34,920 --> 00:41:36,240
The hospital made him read that notice.

855
00:41:36,240 --> 00:41:37,800
He must feel awful too.

856
00:41:40,600 --> 00:41:41,720
Let's have dinner together tonight.

857
00:41:42,200 --> 00:41:43,160
I'll ask Xiaofeng.

858
00:41:43,760 --> 00:41:44,160
Okay.

859
00:41:47,720 --> 00:41:48,800
You didn't bring Xiaorui?

860
00:41:50,400 --> 00:41:51,480
Xiaorui isn't home.

861
00:41:51,640 --> 00:41:52,280
He's at school.

862
00:41:52,840 --> 00:41:53,560
Please enjoy.

863
00:42:02,480 --> 00:42:03,880
It's nothing serious.

864
00:42:04,400 --> 00:42:05,400
Come on, let's eat.

865
00:42:05,840 --> 00:42:07,720
Yes, yes. Eat.

866
00:42:10,920 --> 00:42:11,520
Brother.

867
00:42:11,960 --> 00:42:13,520
I know you're feeling terrible,

868
00:42:14,080 --> 00:42:15,200
