871
00:42:21,880 --> 00:42:22,760
That's just how he is.

872
00:42:22,760 --> 00:42:23,560
Too honest.

873
00:42:23,800 --> 00:42:24,520
Whatever the leaders tell him to do,

874
00:42:24,640 --> 00:42:25,280
