875
00:42:25,520 --> 00:42:26,280
He's nothing like me.

876
00:42:26,320 --> 00:42:26,840
I'm slippery.

877
00:42:26,840 --> 00:42:27,920
I just slide right past things.

878
00:42:34,200 --> 00:42:35,520
When President Cui spoke to me,

879
00:42:37,040 --> 00:42:37,840
