881
00:42:40,720 --> 00:42:42,120
But the hospital office could issue it too.

882
00:42:44,400 --> 00:42:45,520
She respected my choice.

883
00:42:48,520 --> 00:42:49,800
I chose to issue it myself.

884
00:42:51,720 --> 00:42:52,400
Why?

885
00:42:54,080 --> 00:42:55,280
At the inquiry meeting,

886
00:42:55,280 --> 00:42:56,720
